title: Go To Joe 30330, Luke Wilson? 4.9.20
itunes:title: Go To Joe 30330, Luke Wilson? 4.9.20
description:
In episode 605, Jack and Miles are joined by comedian Guy Montgomery to discuss Bernie Sanders dropping out of presidential campaign, coronavirus updates, Trump removing the independent watchdog for coronavirus funds, Jared Kushner wanting to create a national surveillance state for healthcare, Luke Wilson, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. Bernie Sanders Drops Out of 2020 Democratic Race for President
  2. Coronavirus Live Updates: Record Number of New York Deaths; W.H.O. Warns Against Politics
  3. Trump removes independent watchdog for coronavirus funds, upending oversight panel
  4. Kushner’s team seeks national coronavirus surveillance system
  5. Tested positive for coronavirus? Health workers may share your address with police
  6. We'll Never Stop Fighting For America's Small Business Owners!
  7. Luke Wilson
  8. WATCH: Puma Blue - (She's) Just A Phase [official video]
